    "## 2. Exercises & Solutions\n",
    "\n",
    "### Exercise 1:\n",
    "Given the function $L = (x \\cdot w) + b$ and $x=2.0, w=-3.0, b=1.0$, compute the analytical gradients $\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial x}$ and $\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial w}$.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Solution:\n",
    "- $\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial x} = w = -3.0$\n",
    "- $\\frac{\\partial L}{\\partial w} = x = 2.0$"
  }
